room_title: Escape room "Champagne Room" by Escape Artist Texas in Houston
room_description: This is no ordinary mission: your partner, Agent 96, has been undercover for months, pretending to be an exotic dancer Candy. In an attempt to infiltrate the drug lord's circle, she's been working exclusively in the Champagne Room. Before finishing her assignment, she left you a note with clues to where she hid the evidence. Can you find the dirty money and escape before the drug lord returns?
